---
/**
 * A numbered procedure / method — a vertical ribbon of steps, visually distinct
 * from a prose `<ol>`. Wrap `<Step>` children; the markup is a real ordered list
 * so it stays semantic and screen-reader friendly. Numbering is a scoped CSS
 * counter (reset here), so multiple `<Steps>` blocks on a page each start at 1.
 */
---

<ol class="steps"><slot /></ol>

<style>
  .steps {
    counter-reset: step;
    margin-block: var(--space-5);
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }
</style>
